data.description: Perfect starter home for small family or first time home buyers. Large yard is fully fenced in. Plenty of room to build a gazeebo and add additional sheds for storage.  Start planning your large family gatherings as there is plenty of room for the big festivities. Close proximity to Lackland AFB, Shopping Center and lots of Restaurants. Don't miss out on the opportunity to view this charming home. Schedule your showing today!
